stdyInfo.abstract: GFPcro BSC-40 cells were infected at a MOI = 5 with a virus encoding mCherry-tagged to the I1 protein (VACV-I1L-mCherry), and tracked using live cell microscopy to detect the appearance of intermediate stage mCherry protein.
